"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1642613701,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"0knSyiZmDRF7d5H1xfwfEsBTF8xwxvEMRJMWx4Au1YI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x4514F5bCe5c40FE3AC8Bb8B924b99a30d63cE431\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"K170O2yIfAstudIcISFVbPwFUCjcTATiERxKsLQI4NU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"p6nyX723y50MDGB_zD-SmqHHWV-WwounJs6bxw3oq9o\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"XDQX3teTAfy1JDq2VjlFZvEjrVGj31PhgIpBVd8JxyZ-L6755adAuIx3LC1iCbV3XnxJWqaw_BZiSYedomkzNw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xa50e8c53f62cf8079cb5785417f925062981fe61ccdce6579d8053dff77e6e0c5c46503b0fe6ce08fcfe760e188c2c367672cfe4b086f2c6f34a827c644d6c6a1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"K170O2yIfAstudIcISFVbPwFUCjcTATiERxKsLQI4NU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"p6nyX723y50MDGB_zD-SmqHHWV-WwounJs6bxw3oq9o\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi